OL,3,CWhat will a change of Prime Minister
OL,4,Cmean for the North East?
OL,6,FOur new Prime Minister will enter
OL,7,FDowning Street later this month,
OL,8,Ffollowing Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,9,Fresignation.
OL,11,FAndy Burnham is poised to take charge,
OL,12,Fpromising greater devolution, a new
OL,13,FNumber 10 North and "good growth in
OL,14,Fevery British postcode." The change of
OL,15,Fpower at the top of government will
OL,16,Faffect us all, as the new PM tries to
OL,17,Fmake rapid progress to bring about his
OL,18,Fvision.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
