OL,3,CWhat will a change of Prime Minister
OL,4,Cmean for the North East?
OL,6,FTom Sheldrick's panel set out their
OL,7,Fhopes and concerns, including the cost
OL,8,Fof living and the role of elected
OL,9,FMayors.
OL,11,FAlso on the programme - the
OL,12,Fgovernment's long-awaited Defence
OL,13,FInvestment Plan. One of the challenges
OL,14,Ffacing Andy Burnham will be to find
OL,15,Fnearly #5bn to fill a hole in the
OL,16,Fnearly #300bn plans. The Ministry of
OL,17,FDefence is promising it will boost
OL,18,FBritish industry and skills with MPs
OL,19,Fin our region lobbying for contracts
OL,20,Fto be placed here.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/3
